  "title": "ISic003199. Record of tomb purchase by Gerontios",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4MCP2PVV\">http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4MCP2PVV</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>☧ <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γερον\n                    τίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Γερον\n                    τίου\">Γερον-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>τίου</span></span> ἀγο <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span> ρασία </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4MCP2PVV\">http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/4MCP2PVV</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>☧<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Γερον\n                    τίου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Γερον\n                    τίου\">ΓΕΡΟΝ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΤΙΟΥ</span></span>ΑΓΟ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ΡΑΣΙΑ</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of Libertini</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>((Christogram)). Purchase of Gerontios</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Libertini infers that the inscription refers to the group of 6 tombs located a short distance to the east, but there seems no basis for this other than proximity of the find.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 04.0060 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Libertini NSA 1924 108 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
